&lt;p&gt;Every option get saved uppon exiting Options menu.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/nezvers/Godot-GameTemplate/blob/master/Img/Options.png?raw=true"&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/nezvers/Godot-GameTemplate/raw/master/Img/Options.png?raw=true" alt="" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
